eedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vnl1665703533718.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vnl1665703533718.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vnl1665703533718.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vnl1665703533718\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">When you install Uniface on Unix, the installation program generates a shell script called <span class=\"ph filepath\">insunis</span> that defines Uniface’s environment variables.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vnl1665703533718__section_w6696ab1b5b1_w6697ab1b5_w6698ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vnl1665703533718__d6856e17\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Default location:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceAPSInstallDir</var>/common/adm</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vnl1665703533718__section_w6699ab1b5b3_w6700ab1b5_w6701ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1168146e83\">Description </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Environment Variables Defined in <span class=\"ph filepath\">insunis</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__1\">\n Environment Variable\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">urouter</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__2\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">urouter.sh</span> (Unix and\n                        Linux) —Uniface Router executable </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__2\">Uniface executable </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">urm</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__2\">Resource manager executable </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__2\">Directory containing Uniface system components </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USYSADM</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__2\">Directory containing Uniface assignment files;\n                        can be overridden with the <code class=\"ph codeph\">/adm</code> flag </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USYSBIN</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__2\">Directory containing Uniface executables </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USYSLIB</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__2\">Directory containing dynamically loadable\n                        libraries, or shared objects </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USYSINS</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__2\">Uniface installation directory </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USYSCOM</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__2\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">common</span> directory </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USYSUNIFACE</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vnl1665703533718__table_d18572e1_d18573e1_d18574e1__entry__2\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">uniface</span> directory </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vnl1665703533718__section_w6702ab1b5b5_w6703ab1b5_w6704ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1168146e243\">Unix </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vnl1665703533718__p_d176177e1_d176178e1_d176179e1\">To set the environment variables, <span class=\"ph filepath\">insunis</span> must be executed from either the <span class=\"ph filepath\">/etc/profile file</span> or the individual user’s <span class=\"ph filepath\">.profile</span> file.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vnl1665703533718__p_d176180e1_d176181e1_d176182e1\">To set these variables globally, ensure that the <span class=\"ph filepath\">/etc/profile</span> file contains the following:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">. {<var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceInstallationDirectory</var>}/common/insunis[<var class=\"keyword varname\">Id</var>]</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eiq1665702549359.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/adm</a><p>Specify the directory where the application's configuration files are located.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533097\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533097\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "insunis Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 When you install Uniface on Unix, the installation program generates a shell script called insunis that defines Uniface’s environment variables. Default location: UnifaceAPSInstallDir /common/adm Description Table 1. Environment Variables Defined in insunis Environment Variable Description urouter urouter.sh (Unix and Linux) —Uniface Router executable uniface Uniface executable urm Resource manager executable USYS Directory containing Uniface system components USYSADM Directory containing Uniface assignment files; can be overridden with the /adm flag USYSBIN Directory containing Uniface executables USYSLIB Directory containing dynamically loadable libraries, or shared objects USYSINS Uniface installation directory USYSCOM common directory USYSUNIFACE uniface directory Unix To set the environment variables, insunis must be executed from either the /etc/profile file or the individual user’s .profile file. To set these variables globally, ensure that the /etc/profile file contains the following: . { UnifaceInstallationDirectory }/common/insunis[ Id ] Copy Related Links /adm Specify the directory where the application's configuration files are located. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}